Homepage: https://caddyserver.com
Description: Caddy - Fast, extensible multi-platform HTTP/1-2-3 web server
 Caddy is a powerful, enterprise-ready, open source web server with
 automatic HTTPS written in Go.
 .
 This is a custom multi-architecture build with additional plugins:
  - caddy-webdav: WebDAV module for Caddy
  - caddy-cgi: CGI support for Caddy
  - caddy-exec: Run external commands from Caddy
